		<p>Downstairs, Mitch was considering asking them to turn the music down, but as he reached the first step, he suddenly reconsidered. Instead, he headed towards his own bedroom, to find something hidden away in his sock drawer.</p>
		<hr/>
		<p>When Dawson unlocked his door, he was surprised to find his father on the other side, his hand raised as if about to knock.</p>
