		<p>"It's beautiful," Joey said, feeling a little awe-struck.</p>
		<p>Going into someone else's room for the first time was always a little like being in a foreign country, but this was like a whole other world. Joey circled the room slowly, examining things. There were several paintings stacked in the corner, facing the wall.</p>
