		<hr/>
		<p>It was after midnight when Pacey dropped Dawson off at his house. He slipped out of the truck as quietly as he could, closing the door lightly. "Think Mitch and Gale will be mad?" Pacey asked, hoping his plans for tomorrow night wouldn't be foiled by Dawson's absence.</p>
