		<p>"All right, see you in the morning, then." Pacey pulled out slowly, trying not to draw any attention to the rattling truck, and drove off. Dawson started towards his door, but then he noticed someone sitting on the dock. it wouldn't be Joey-- she always waited in his bedroom, usually in the closet. He went over to see who it was; after all, it was past midnight.</p>
